            <div type="edition" subtype="diplomatic" ana="b1">
                <p><lb/>ΕΠΙΤΟΥ <lb/><gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="1"/>ΓΣ ΜΑΚΑΡΙΟΤΣ
                        <lb/><unclear>Ι</unclear>ΜΩΝΠΑΤΡΚ<gap reason="lost" unit="character"
                        extent="1"/>
                    <lb/>ΕΠΙΣΚΜΕΓΑ<del rend="erasure">Λ</del>Σ<gap reason="lost" unit="character"
                        extent="1"/>
                    <lb/>ΕΓΕΝΕΤΟΤΟΠ<gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="2"/>
                    <lb/>ΕΡΓΟΝΤΗΣΨΗ <lb/>ΦΩΣΕΩΣΤ<hi rend="ligature">ΟΥ</hi>ΑΦΣ <lb/>ΜΑΡΤΥΡΘΕΟ
                    <lb/>ΔΩΡΟΥ</p>
            </div>
            <div type="edition" subtype="transcription" ana="b1">
                <p>Ἐπὶ τοῦ <lb/><expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost"
                            >ἁ</supplied>γ</abbr><ex>ίου</ex></expan>
                    <expan><abbr>κ</abbr><ex>αὶ</ex></expan>
                    <choice><corr><expan><abbr>μακαριοτ</abbr><ex>άτου</ex></expan></corr><sic><expan><abbr>μακαριοτ</abbr><ex>άτου</ex></expan></sic></choice>
                    <lb/><unclear>ἡ</unclear>μῶν <expan><abbr>πατρ</abbr><ex>ὸς</ex></expan>
                    <expan><abbr>κ</abbr><supplied reason="lost"><ex>αὶ</ex></supplied></expan>
                    <lb/><expan>ἐπισκόπου</expan> Μεγά<del rend="erasure"
                        >λ</del><unclear>ο</unclear><supplied reason="lost">υ</supplied>
                    <lb/>ἐγενετο τὸ π<unclear>ᾶ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ν</supplied>
                    <lb/>ἔργον τῆς ψη<lb break="no"/>φώσες τ<hi rend="ligature">οῦ</hi>
                    <expan><abbr>ἁγ</abbr><ex>ίου</ex></expan>
                    <lb/><expan><abbr>μαρτυρ</abbr><ex>ίου</ex></expan> Θεο<lb break="no"/>δώρου</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>Under our holy and truly blessed father and bishop Megas, the entire work of the
                    mosaic in the holy martyrion of Theodoros was executed.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p>Staab and Eisenberg understand this church to be a martyrion dedicated to
                    Theodoros Tiron of Amaseia. </p>
            </div>
        </body>
